Man Numeric














Man Numeric
Established, institutional manager focused on maximizing alpha for clients
Employs disciplined, systematic investment processes that are underpinned by a robust fundamental approach
Highly experienced investment professionals enhance and complement the quantitative process
Significant focus on capacity management and efficient implementation
Benefits from Man Group’s high-quality infrastructure and strong balance sheet
Global client base with many long-standing relationships
 













