Numeric Investors LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 9:02 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Numeric Investors LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Numeric Investors LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to high net worth individuals, corporate pension and profit-sharing plans, Taft-Hartley plans, charitable institutions, foundations, endowments, municipalities, private investment funds, trust programs, sovereign funds, foreign funds such as UCITS and SICAV funds, and other U.S. and international institutions. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It manages equity mutual funds. The firm also launches and manages hedge funds. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. ...
Numeric Investors LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to high net worth individuals, corporate pension and profit-sharing plans, Taft-Hartley plans, charitable institutions, foundations, endowments, municipalities, private investment funds, trust programs, sovereign funds, foreign funds such as UCITS and SICAV funds, and other U.S. and international institutions. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It manages equity mutual funds. The firm also launches and manages hedge funds. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. Numeric Investors LLC was founded in 1989 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts Numeric Investors LLC operates as a subsidiary of Numeric Midco LLC.
Detailed Description


470 Atlantic Avenue6th FloorBoston, MA 02210United StatesFounded in 1989



